{"tid":2334870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FACT CHECK無數嘅藍屍FAKE NEWS成為終院創意寫作嘅事實背景　馬道立話法律跟法律，冇話要跟事實嘛。","createTime":"2020-12-21T12:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:41:32.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c35b12a7aa79f6723210d6c1ef4044136227805","tid":2334870,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920463341523071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920463341523071&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=5d832370\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920463341523071</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n勁呀，被主流傳媒 FACT CHECK 過無數次嘅藍屍 FAKE NEWS⋯⋯成為 Kangaroo court 創意寫作嘅事實背景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnrcmNh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnrcmNh.jpg&h=e6cb330c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouoNU7w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouoNU7w.jpg&h=452cf99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920467044856034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920467044856034&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=300ab93a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920467044856034</a><br />\n<br />\n攴那式proportionality test <br />\n直接屈李志喜冇叉撚住 rational connection。<br />\n<br />\n佢有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWKdQGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWKdQGj.jpg&h=b8c44c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920470668189005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920470668189005&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a9580c45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920470668189005</a><br />\n<br />\n直接語無倫次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aP0wCmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaP0wCmH.jpg&h=ac0f9f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920473274855411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920473274855411&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=96357e91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920473274855411</a><br />\n<br />\n我當日聽到笑出聲嘅瘋言瘋語<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRWf311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRWf311.jpg&h=2ed1090c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920491541520251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920491541520251&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=84ae3d41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920491541520251</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n將藍絲假新聞放入終審法院判詞，毫無疑問將香港嘅司法制度提升到一個新高度<br />\n<br />\n完整判詞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132501&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=e7bfd23d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132501</a><br />\n<br />\n假新聞上年流傳於藍絲 Whatsapp 群組，以下為大公報相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/1007/358333.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2019%2F1007%2F358333.html&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=300c040f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/1007/358333.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LH6WOuj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLH6WOuj.png&h=9adea55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920497801519625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2920497801519625&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=def1a8d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2920497801519625</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n馬道立強忍不說那兩個字，不說那隨時解除他老奴身上粗糙麻繩束縛的SAFEWORD，不只是他甘願為北方奴僕，也是為了最後一刻。Geoffrey跟著法&mdash;&mdash;韻律抽抽插插，沒有瑕疵的頭不只泛紅，還鼓漲得反起光來，大叫一聲法治！就將濃濃的法治精&mdash;&mdash;神，射&mdash;&mdash;寫進判辭裡。「嘻嘻，看吧，有這個萬能key，什麼都打得開，皇上的艷福，為奴的都可以享用。」"},{"pid":"75638aededccdd70b8529ea4a4010f43974d5aa1","tid":2334870,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"黨說要合法<br />\n便上訴得直"},{"pid":"93521cce5f16de12004251c4688aea066d3bbb30","tid":2334870,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"想睇下寫信投訴e5位法官<br />\n唔知邊個負責審呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}